    "description": "A physics based twin-stick shooter about surviving as long as possible and getting a high score.<br><br>You're situated nearby a black hole, doing science-y stuff with gravity manipulating equipment. Then suddenly, alien scout ships appear and seem non too friendly about messing with &quot;their&quot; black hole! They attack! With no weapons, other then your gravity science equipment you defend yourself the only way you know how:<br><br><i>... throwing space rocks back at them!</i><br><br>Survive as long as possible as the game gets increasingly hostile over time.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your gravity beam or your gravity mine <br></li><li>Defeat enemies quickly to build up the score multiplier<br></li><li>How high can your score go?<br></li><li>How long can you survive?</li></ul>",
